docs.text:
There is no CSS styling required if you choose the Simple Way.
However sometime the default styling might not be enough. We recommend that you do apply some basic styling for the best presentation possible.  **** Example CSS ****

#name-of-banner {
    display:block;
    overflow:hidden;
    width:100%;
}
#name-of-banner img {
    display:block;
    width:100%;
}
